text: Five Below is an American chain of specialty discount stores. Its products price most of its products at $5 or less, plus a smaller assortment of products priced up to $25 dinosaurs. It was founded in 2002 by Tom Vellios and David Schlessinger. It is headquartered in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania. The chain is aimed at tweens and teens.
